# Mangia-Tutti Restaurant Website

## Overview
A responsive, SEO-friendly website built for **Mangia-Tutti**, an Italian restaurant in San Francisco.  
The site improves the restaurantâ€™s **online visibility** and provides a smooth **customer experience** for browsing the menu.

## Features
- Fully responsive design (mobile, tablet, desktop)
- Clean, modern restaurant branding
- SEO optimization for better search rankings
- Menu integration with easy updates
- Social media links and customer engagement tools

## Tech Stack
- HTML5  
- CSS3 (Flexbox & Grid)  
- JavaScript  
- Git & GitHub  
- Hosting: GitHub Pages

